search_results.title: Rhulani Mokwena
search_results.snippet: Rhulani Mlungisi Mokwena (born 9 January 1987) is a South African football manager. He last managed Botola side Wydad AC.

search_results.title: Rhulani Baloyi - SAMBT
search_results.snippet: Rhulani is both a radio and television journalist. She is the talk show presenter of SAFM radio's Intune, which broadcasts live every Saturday.
